  <brief_title>Empagliflozin-based Quadruple Combination vs Insulin Glarine-based Combination Therapy in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Empagliflozin vs. Insulin Glargine add-on Therapy in Patients With Inadequately Controlled Type 2 Diabetes Under Triple Combination Therapy</official_title>
